            <history-note id="DLM369052"><amended-provision>Section 8(1A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>15 April 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM221488">section 11(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Criminal Investigations (Bodily Samples) Amendment Act 2003</amending-leg> (2003 No 113).</history-note>
