            <history-note id="DLM369264"><amended-provision>Section 30(1)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>15 April 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM221481">section 6</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Criminal Investigations (Bodily Samples) Amendment Act 2003</amending-leg> (2003 No 113).</history-note>
