            <history-note id="DLM1676710"><amended-provision>Section 47(1)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1102383">section 130(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Policing Act 2008</amending-leg> (2008 No 72).</history-note>
